name: volumio-phishin
description: A Phish.in plugin for Volumio2. Play over 1,500 live Phish audience recordings from Phish.in..  Phish.in and the Volumio Phish.in music service plugin complies with Phish's official taping policy as described at http://phish.com/#/faq/taping-guidelines.
author: Noah McGee (lostmyshape)
